Parallel-SubFork version 0.01
=============================

This module provides a simple way to execute arbitrary perl code from different
processes through the fork system call.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

	perl Makefile.PL
	make
	make test
	make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module depends on the following CPAN modules:

	Carp
	POSIX
	Class::Accessor::Fast

